long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
It's my first extension just for fun, maybe we can finding somehow usage, why not!

Features:
--------------
1. Popup news list for SAP.info 
2. SAP cmd prefix /n, /o for open URL in currently tab(/n) or NEW tab(/o)
3. prefix /h for Help to open SAP Note(enter note number), OR search SAP Notes & SAP Community Network parallel (enter key words).

Readme:
--------------
http://sap.song.tw/2011/07/sapor.html
